# BankingSystem

BankingSystem is a simple banking application project that demonstrates an MVC-style model package with accounts, customers, and transaction types.

## Structure

- `src/` — source package root
- `src/models/` — domain model classes
- `tests/` — automated tests
- `docs/` — documentation and design notes
